attributes.text: At the roundabout, take the first exit onto Grassie Blvd
Take the exit on the right to MB-101 W / Perimeter Hwy
Keep left at the fork to merge onto Perimeter Hwy (MB-101)
Take exit 60B-A on the right to City Rte-90 / MB-7 toward Stonewall / Brookside Blvd
Keep left at the fork to Provincial Trunk Highway 7 (MB-7)
Keep right at the fork to merge onto Provincial Trunk Highway 7 (MB-7)
Continue forward on Brookside Blvd (City Rte-90)
At the traffic light, continue forward on Centreport Canada Way (MB-190)
At the traffic light, make a sharp left on Sturgeon Rd
At the stop sign, make a sharp left on Sturgeon Rd
Turn right to stay on Sturgeon Rd
At the roundabout, take the second exit onto Sturgeon Rd
Finish at Location 2, on the right
